    renderProjectSummary();
    alert("Profile saved.");
  }
  function clearProfile(){
    localStorage.removeItem("hbl_profile_off");
    ["firstName","lastName","projAddr","docName"].forEach(id=>$(id).value="");
    renderProjectSummary();
  }
  function renderProjectSummary(){
    const p = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("hbl_profile_off")||"{}");
    const parts = [];
    if(p.firstName || p.lastName) parts.push("<b>Client:</b> " + (p.firstName||"") + " " + (p.lastName||""));
    if(p.projAddr) parts.push("<b>Address:</b> " + p.projAddr);
    if(p.docName) parts.push("<b>Building Doctor:</b> " + p.docName);
    $("projectSummary").innerHTML = parts.length? parts.join(" &nbsp; | &nbsp; ") : "No identity saved.";
  }

  function computeMedalAndShow(){
    const badge = $("medalBadge");
    const alarmBadge = $("alarmMedal");
    const latest = records[records.length-1];
    if(!latest){ badge.classList.add("hidden"); alarmBadge.classList.add("hidden"); return; }
    // Normalize weights only for filled metrics
    let totalW=0, score=0;
    for(const k of METRIC_ORDER){
      const val = latest.metrics?.[k];
      if(val!=null && !isNaN(val)){
        totalW += (WEIGHTS[k]||0);
        score += (WEIGHTS[k]||0) * (scoreOfStatus(statusOf(k,val)));
      }
    }
    const norm = totalW>0 ? score/totalW : 0;
    let grade="BRONZE", cls="bronze";
    if(norm>=0.75){ grade="GOLD"; cls="gold"; }
    else if(norm>=0.50){ grade="SILVER"; cls="silver"; }
    else { grade="BRONZE"; cls="bronze"; }
    badge.textContent = grade;
    badge.className = "medal " + cls;
    alarmBadge.textContent = grade;
    alarmBadge.className = "medal " + cls;
  }

  function saveRecord(){
    const rec = {
      id: (Math.random()+"").slice(2),
      ts: new Date().toISOString(),
      project: $("mProject").value.trim(),
      zone: $("mZone").value.trim(),
      device: $("mDevice").value,
      metrics: {
        temp: parseNum($("mTemp").value), rh: parseNum($("mRH").value), co2: parseNum($("mCO2").value),
        pm25: parseNum($("mPM25").value), pm10: parseNum($("mPM10").value), voc: parseNum($("mVOC").value),
        noise: parseNum($("mNoise").value), lux: parseNum($("mLux").value), wbgt: parseNum($("mWBGT").value),
        radon: parseNum($("mRadon").value), tds: parseNum($("mTDS").value),
      }
    };
    records.push(rec);
    localStorage.setItem("hbl_recs_off", JSON.stringify(records));
    ["mProject","mZone","mTemp","mRH","mCO2","mPM25","mPM10","mVOC","mNoise","mLux","mWBGT","mRadon","mTDS"].forEach(id=>$(id).value="");
    $("mTs").value = new Date().toLocaleString();
    document.querySelector('[data-tab="analytics"]').click();
    renderAll();
    alert("Record added.");
  }
  window.__DEL__ = (id)=>{ records = records.filter(r=>r.id!=id); localStorage.setItem("hbl_recs_off", JSON.stringify(records)); renderAll(); };

  function renderDashboard(){
    const latest = records[records.length-1];
    const vals = latest? latest.metrics : {};
    const map = {temp:"val-temp", rh:"val-rh", co2:"val-co2", pm25:"val-pm25", voc:"val-voc"};
    Object.entries(map).forEach(([k,id])=>{
      const el = $(id); const b = $("badge-"+k);
      const v = vals?k in vals?vals[k]:null:null;
      el.textContent = (v==null||isNaN(v)) ? "â€”" : v;
      const st = statusOf(k, v);
      b.textContent = st;
      b.className = "badge " + (st==="Good"?"b-ok":st==="Attention"?"b-warn":st==="Poor"?"b-bad":"");
    });

    const alarms = [];
    for(const r of records.slice(-200)){
      for(const k of METRIC_ORDER){
        const v = r.metrics?.[k]; if(v==null||isNaN(v)) continue;
        const st = statusOf(k,v);
        if(st==="Attention"||st==="Poor"){
          const warnStr = (META[k].warn||[]).map(rr=>rr.join("â€“")).join(" / ");
          alarms.push({ priority: st==="Poor" ? "U" : "H", ts: new Date(r.ts).toLocaleString(),
            zone: r.zone||"-", device: r.device||"-", type: META[k].label,
            value: v + " " + (META[k].unit||""), limit: warnStr + " " + (META[k].unit||"") });
        }
      }
    }
    $("alarm-total").textContent = alarms.length;
    $("alarm-urgent").textContent = alarms.filter(a=>a.priority==="U").length;
    $("alarm-high").textContent   = alarms.filter(a=>a.priority==="H").length;

    const tbody = $("alarmBody");
    tbody.innerHTML = alarms.length? alarms.slice(0,40).map(a=>
      `<tr><td>${a.priority}</td><td>${a.ts}</td><td>${a.zone}</td><td>${a.device}</td><td>${a.type}</td><td>${a.value}</td><td>${a.limit}</td></tr>`
    ).join("") : `<tr><td colspan="7" style="color:var(--muted)">No data yet.</td></tr>`;

    // Show medal after first record (alarm card & identity)
    computeMedalAndShow();
  }

  function renderHistory(){
    const tbody = $("histBody");
    if(records.length===0){
      tbody.innerHTML = `<tr><td colspan="6" style="color:var(--muted)">No data yet.</td></tr>`;
      return;
    }
    tbody.innerHTML = records.slice().reverse().map(r=>{
      const metrics = METRIC_ORDER.map(k=>r.metrics?.[k]).some(v=>v!=null)
        ? METRIC_ORDER.map(k=>{ const v=r.metrics?.[k]; return (v!=null&&!isNaN(v))? `<span class='chip'>${META[k].label}: ${v} ${META[k].unit}</span>`: "" }).join(" ")
        : "-";
      return `<tr>
        <td>${new Date(r.ts).toLocaleString()}</td>
        <td>${r.project||""}</td>
        <td>${r.zone||""}</td>
        <td>${r.device||""}</td>
        <td>${metrics}</td>
        <td><button onclick="__DEL__('${r.id}')">Delete</button></td>
      </tr>`;
    }).join("");
  }

  // -------- Minimal chart utilities (no external libs) ----------
  function clearCanvas(c){ const ctx=c.getContext("2d"); ctx.fillStyle="#111518"; ctx.fillRect(0,0,c.width,c.height); return ctx; }
  function drawAxes(ctx, x, y, w, h){ ctx.strokeStyle="#ddd"; ctx.lineWidth=1; ctx.strokeRect(x,y,w,h); }
  function map(v, a,b, c,d){ return c + (v-a)*(d-c)/(b-a || 1); }

  function lineChart(canvas, labels, data, color){
    const ctx = clearCanvas(canvas);
    const pad = 40, x=pad, y=20, w=canvas.width-2*pad, h=canvas.height-60;
    drawAxes(ctx,x,y,w,h);
    const min = Math.min(...data, 0), max = Math.max(...data, 1);
    ctx.strokeStyle=color||"#0ea5e9"; ctx.lineWidth=2; ctx.beginPath();
    data.forEach((v,i)=>{
      const px = x + (w*(i/(data.length-1||1)));
      const py = y + h - map(v,min,max,0,h);
      if(i===0) ctx.moveTo(px,py); else ctx.lineTo(px,py);
    });
    ctx.stroke();
    ctx.fillStyle="#444"; ctx.font="12px sans-serif";
    const step = Math.max(1, Math.floor(labels.length/6));
    labels.forEach((lab,i)=>{ if(i%step===0){ ctx.fillText(lab, x + (w*(i/(labels.length-1||1))) - 20, y+h+18); } });
  }

  
function barChart(canvas, labels, stacks, colors){
  // kept for compatibility if called
  return groupedBarChart(canvas, labels, stacks, colors);
}
function groupedBarChart(canvas, labels, stacks, colors){

    const ctx = clearCanvas(canvas);
    const pad = 40, x=pad, y=20, w=canvas.width-2*pad, h=canvas.height-60;
    drawAxes(ctx,x,y,w,h);
    const groups = labels.length;
    const series = stacks[0] ? stacks[0].length : 0;
    const groupW = w/groups*0.8;
    const barW = (groupW/(series||1))*0.8;
    // compute global max across all values
    const max = Math.max(...stacks.flat(), 1);
    labels.forEach((lab,i)=>{
      for(let si=0; si<series; si++){
        const val = stacks[i][si] || 0;
        const bh = (val/max)*h;
        const bx = x + i*(w/groups) + (w/groups - groupW)/2 + si*(groupW/series) + (groupW/series - barW)/2;
        ctx.fillStyle = colors[si];
        ctx.fillRect(bx, y+h - bh, barW, bh);
      }
      ctx.fillStyle="#bbb"; ctx.font="12px sans-serif"; ctx.fillText(lab, x + i*(w/groups)+ (w/groups-groupW)/2, y+h+18);
    });
  }

  function radarChart(canvas, labels, data){
    const ctx = clearCanvas(canvas);
    const cx = canvas.width/2, cy = canvas.height/2, r = Math.min(cx,cy)-30;
    const n = labels.length;
    ctx.strokeStyle="#ddd"; ctx.beginPath();
    for(let k=1;k<=4;k++){ ctx.beginPath(); for(let i=0;i<n;i++){ const a=(i/n)*2*Math.PI; const rr=r*k/4; const px=cx+rr*Math.cos(a- Math.PI/2); const py=cy+rr*Math.sin(a- Math.PI/2); if(i===0)ctx.moveTo(px,py); else ctx.lineTo(px,py);} ctx.closePath(); ctx.stroke(); }
    // labels
    ctx.fillStyle="#333"; ctx.font="12px sans-serif";
    labels.forEach((lab,i)=>{ const a=(i/n)*2*Math.PI; const px=cx+(r+10)*Math.cos(a- Math.PI/2); const py=cy+(r+10)*Math.sin(a- Math.PI/2); ctx.fillText(lab, px-20, py); });
    // data polygon (normalize to [0,1])
    const max = Math.max(...data,1);
    ctx.fillStyle="rgba(16,185,129,0.25)"; ctx.strokeStyle="#10b981"; ctx.beginPath();
    data.forEach((v,i)=>{ const a=(i/n)*2*Math.PI; const rr=r*(v/max); const px=cx+rr*Math.cos(a- Math.PI/2); const py=cy+rr*Math.sin(a- Math.PI/2); if(i===0)ctx.moveTo(px,py); else ctx.lineTo(px,py); });
    ctx.closePath(); ctx.fill(); ctx.stroke();
  }

  function benchmarkChart(canvas, labels, latestVals, goodRanges){
    const ctx = clearCanvas(canvas);
    const pad = 40, x=pad, y=20, w=canvas.width-2*pad, h=canvas.height-60;
    drawAxes(ctx,x,y,w,h);
    const groups = labels.length;
    const barW = w/groups*0.35;
    const max = Math.max(...latestVals, ...goodRanges.map(g=>g[1]), 1);
    labels.forEach((lab,i)=>{
      const gx = x + i*(w/groups) + (w/groups)/2;
      // good band
      const gmin = goodRanges[i][0], gmax=goodRanges[i][1];
      const gy1 = y+h - (gmin/max)*h, gy2 = y+h - (gmax/max)*h;
      ctx.fillStyle="rgba(148,163,184,0.4)"; ctx.fillRect(gx - barW, gy2, barW*2, gy1-gy2);
      // latest
      const bh = (latestVals[i]/max)*h; ctx.fillStyle="rgba(14,165,233,0.85)"; ctx.fillRect(gx - barW/2, y+h - bh, barW, bh);
      ctx.fillStyle="#444"; ctx.font="12px sans-serif"; ctx.fillText(lab, gx - 20, y+h+18);
    });
  }

  function summarize(){
    const summary = {};
    for(const k of METRIC_ORDER){
      const vals = records.map(r=>r.metrics?.[k]).filter(v=>v!=null&&!isNaN(v));
      if(!vals.length) continue;
      const min = Math.min(...vals), max = Math.max(...vals);
      const avg = vals.reduce((p,c)=>p+c,0)/vals.length;
      let g=0,w=0,p=0;
      for(const v of vals){ const s=statusOf(k,v); if(s==="Good") g++; else if(s==="Attention") w++; else if(s==="Poor") p++; }
      summary[k] = { count:vals.length, min, max, avg, dist:{Good:g,Attention:w,Poor:p} };
    }
    return summary;
  }

  function renderTrend(metric){/* removed */ return;
    const c = $("trendChart");
    const pts = records.filter(r=>r.metrics && r.metrics[metric]!=null && !isNaN(r.metrics[metric]))
                       .map(r=>({l: new Date(r.ts).toLocaleTimeString(), y: r.metrics[metric]}));
    const labels = pts.length? pts.map(p=>p.l):["No data"];
    const data = pts.length? pts.map(p=>p.y):[0];
    lineChart(c, labels, data, "#0ea5e9");
    $("trendTitle").textContent = META[metric].label;
  }
  function renderRadar(){
    const latest = records[records.length-1]||{metrics:{}};
    const keys = METRIC_ORDER;
    const labels = keys.map(k=>META[k].label);
    const values = keys.map(k=> latest.metrics[k]!=null&&!isNaN(latest.metrics[k]) ? latest.metrics[k] : 0);
    radarChart($("radarChart"), labels, values);
  }
  function renderDistribution(){
    const sum = summarize();
    const labels = Object.keys(sum).map(k=>META[k].label);
    const stacks = Object.values(sum).map(s=>[s.dist.Good, s.dist.Attention, s.dist.Poor]);
    barChart($("distChart"), labels, stacks, ["#22c55e","#f59e0b","#ef4444"]);
  }
  function renderBenchmark(){
    const latest = records[records.length-1];
    const keys = ["temp","rh","co2","pm25","voc"];
    const labels = keys.map(k=>META[k].label);
    const latestVals = keys.map(k=> latest && latest.metrics[k]!=null&&!isNaN(latest.metrics[k]) ? latest.metrics[k] : 0);
    const goodRanges = keys.map(k=> META[k].good[0] || [0,0]);
    benchmarkChart($("benchChart"), labels, latestVals, goodRanges);
  }

  function renderAnalyticsSummary(){
    const sum = summarize();
    const lines = [];
    for(const k of Object.keys(sum)){
      const s = sum[k];
      lines.push("<div>â€¢ <b>"+META[k].label+"</b> â€” avg: "+s.avg.toFixed(2)+" "+META[k].unit+", min: "+s.min+", max: "+s.max+" â€” Good: "+s.dist.Good+", Attention: "+s.dist.Attention+", Poor: "+s.dist.Poor+"</div>");
    }
    $("analyticsSummary").innerHTML = lines.length? lines.join("") : "No data yet.";
  }

  
  function clearAnalyticsCanvases(){
    const ids = ["radarChart","distChart","benchChart"];
    ids.forEach(id=>{
      const c = document.getElementById(id);
      if(c && c.getContext){
        const ctx = c.getContext("2d");
        c.width = c.width; // reset clears
      }
    });
  }
function renderAll(){
    // Only render non-analytics on first load.
    renderProjectSummary();
    renderDashboard();
    renderHistory();
    // Charts will render ONLY when Analytics tab is active (see setupNav).\n    clearAnalyticsCanvases();
  }

  function setupNav(){

      });
      if(tab==="analytics"){  renderRadar(); renderDistribution(); renderBenchmark(); } else { clearAnalyticsCanvases(); }
    }));
  }

  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function(){
    document.getElementById("yr").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();

      document.getElementById("mTs").value = new Date().toLocaleString();

<script>


// === Project Plan & Zoning (polygon) ===
(function(){
  const base = document.getElementById('planCanvas');
  const overlay = document.getElementById('drawCanvas');
  const wrap = document.getElementById('canvasWrap');
  const planFile = document.getElementById('planFile');
  const zoneListDiv = document.getElementById('zoneList');
  const zoneModeBtn = document.getElementById('zoneMode');
  const zoneSaveBtn = document.getElementById('zoneSave');
  const zoneClearBtn = document.getElementById('zoneClear');
  const zoneSelect = document.getElementById('zoneSelect');
  const zoneName = document.getElementById('zoneName');
  const hint = document.getElementById('planHint');
  if(!base) return;

  const ctxBase = base.getContext('2d');
  const ctx = overlay.getContext('2d');
  let img=null, planData = localStorage.getItem('hbl_plan');
  let drawing=false, pts=[];
  let zones = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('hbl_zones')||'[]'); // {name, pts:[{x,y}]}

  function resize(){
    const r = wrap.getBoundingClientRect();
    [base,overlay].forEach(c=>{ c.width=r.width; c.height=Math.max(420, r.height); });
    drawAll();
  }
  window.addEventListener('resize', resize);

  function drawAll(){
    // background + plan
    ctxBase.fillStyle='#0f1318'; ctxBase.fillRect(0,0,base.width, base.height);
    if(img){ 
      // fit contain
      const ratio=Math.min(base.width/img.width, base.height/img.height);
      const w=img.width*ratio, h=img.height*ratio;
      const x=(base.width-w)/2, y=(base.height-h)/2;
      ctxBase.drawImage(img,x,y,w,h);
    }
    // overlay
    ctx.clearRect(0,0,overlay.width, overlay.height);
    ctx.lineWidth=2; ctx.strokeStyle='#38bdf8'; ctx.fillStyle='rgba(56,189,248,0.15)';
    // current poly
    if(pts.length){
      ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(pts[0].x, pts[0].y);
      for(let i=1;i<pts.length;i++) ctx.lineTo(pts[i].x, pts[i].y);
      ctx.stroke();
    }
    // saved zones
    zones.forEach((z,i)=>{
      if(!z.pts||z.pts.length<3) return;
      ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(z.pts[0].x, z.pts[0].y);
      for(let j=1;j<z.pts.length;j++) ctx.lineTo(z.pts[j].x, z.pts[j].y);
      ctx.closePath(); ctx.fill(); ctx.stroke();
      // label
      const cx = z.pts.reduce((a,p)=>a+p.x,0)/z.pts.length;
      const cy = z.pts.reduce((a,p)=>a+p.y,0)/z.pts.length;
      ctx.fillStyle='#e5e7eb'; ctx.font='12px sans-serif'; ctx.fillText(z.name||('Zone '+(i+1)), cx-20, cy);
      ctx.fillStyle='rgba(56,189,248,0.15)';
    });
  }

  overlay.addEventListener('mousedown', e=>{
    if(!drawing) return;
    const b=overlay.getBoundingClientRect();
    pts.push({x:e.clientX-b.left, y:e.clientY-b.top});
    drawAll();
  });
  overlay.addEventListener('dblclick', e=>{
    if(!drawing || pts.length<3) return;
    zones.push({name:(zoneName.value||('Zone '+(zones.length+1))), pts:[...pts]});
    pts.length=0; drawing=false; zoneModeBtn.classList.remove('active');
    refreshZoneList(); updateZoneSelect(); drawAll(); persist();
  });

  zoneModeBtn && zoneModeBtn.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
    drawing = !drawing; pts.length=0;
    zoneModeBtn.classList.toggle('active', drawing);
  });
  zoneClearBtn && zoneClearBtn.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
    if(confirm('Clear all zones?')){
      zones=[]; pts=[]; refreshZoneList(); updateZoneSelect(); drawAll(); persist();
    }
  });
  zoneSaveBtn && zoneSaveBtn.addEventListener('click', persist);

  planFile && planFile.addEventListener('change', e=>{
    const f=e.target.files[0]; if(!f) return;
    const reader=new FileReader();
    reader.onload = ev=>{
      img=new Image(); img.onload=()=>{ planData=ev.target.result; hint && (hint.style.display='none'); drawAll(); persist(); };
      img.src=ev.target.result;
    };
    reader.readAsDataURL(f);
  });

  function refreshZoneList(){
    if(!zoneListDiv) return;
    if(!zones.length){ zoneListDiv.innerHTML='No zones yet.'; return; }
    zoneListDiv.innerHTML='';
    zones.forEach((z,i)=>{
      const row = document.createElement('div');
      row.style.cssText='display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin:4px 0;padding:4px;border:1px solid #2a2f36;border-radius:6px';
      row.innerHTML='<b>'+ (z.name||('Zone '+(i+1))) +'</b><div><button class="btn ghost" data-i="'+i+'">Delete</button></div>';
      row.querySelector('button').onclick = ()=>{ zones.splice(i,1); refreshZoneList(); updateZoneSelect(); drawAll(); persist(); };
      zoneListDiv.appendChild(row);
    });
  }
  function updateZoneSelect(){
    const sel = zoneSelect; if(!sel) return;
    sel.innerHTML = '<option value="">Select zoneâ€¦</option>' + zones.map((z,i)=>{
      const name = z.name || ('Zone '+(i+1));
      return '<option value="'+name+'">'+name+'</option>';
    }).join('');
  }
  function persist(){
    localStorage.setItem('hbl_zones', JSON.stringify(zones));
    if(planData) localStorage.setItem('hbl_plan', planData);
    alert('Saved locally.');
  }

  // load stored plan
  if(planData){
    img = new Image();
    img.onload = ()=>{ hint && (hint.style.display='none'); drawAll(); };
    img.src = planData;
  }
  refreshZoneList(); updateZoneSelect();
  // initial canvas sizing
  setTimeout(resize, 0);
})();
;

</script>
